SSH key:
Master-
create a key pair on the client machine
ssh-keygen
ssh-copy-id node1@192.168.22.133
ssh-copy-id node2@192.168.22.134

Installing ansible:
from master-
sudo apt-add-repository ppa:ansible/ansible
sudo apt update
sudo apt upgrade
sudo apt install ansible

Inventory file setup:
sudo nano /etc/ansible/hosts

